{"tid":1001132,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩辦法除狗狗異味?","createTime":"2019-01-30T02:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T15:18:08.000Z","uid":232742,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5c19e18b62061b1047c31481f1402cfe71ebe6bc","tid":1001132,"uid":232742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:03:39.000Z","msg":"小妹養了兩隻法虎, 分別三和四歲, 每日返工前會帶狗狗散步大小便, 在家也會定點大小便, 約兩星期沖涼一次, 主要吃乾糧, 有時會比生果, 蔬菜, 唔係經常刷牙。每日有吸塵拖地, 有擺放香薰, 剛剛添置左空氣淨化機。<br />\n上星期開始業主/鄰居投訴有異味, 再唔算決就被迫遷, 點算呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abab0d5e9ee178b1ae0e802d83204a633bdc361d","tid":1001132,"uid":134666,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:26:05.000Z","msg":"幫佢地含乾淨"},{"pid":"4dc472bb07138aae978c48ef8773991c205e556a","tid":1001132,"uid":32028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"你覺得係咪有味先, 定係人地玩野"},{"pid":"3acd716a115aa534308190ea269fa263bd25b6c7","tid":1001132,"uid":146376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:03:32.000Z","msg":"幫佢地噴香水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2e196eb2e9fd520fcc35b259815005a652cd87","tid":1001132,"uid":227967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:28:00.000Z","msg":"體味大到咁會唔會係因為有皮膚病?"},{"pid":"0d72906f900ecf406b83c3ba254a8eb5c5197b39","tid":1001132,"uid":76105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4dc472bb07138aae978c48ef8773991c205e556a","tid":1001132,"uid":32028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"你覺得係咪有味先, 定係人地玩野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"當你每日係哩個地方，你會適應咗果種味道。<br />\n你自己聞無味，但人地聞就好撚臭"},{"pid":"17599293293fe1580253edf665dab1e898ee165f","tid":1001132,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"可能問題唔係你隻狗身上，會唔會佢地痾咗屎尿係啲傢私裡面？<br />\n例如梳化，床，一啲木製傢品，牆，搞到啲味滲左入去，咁你點清都無用㗎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你都聞唔到 因為你聞慣，建議你搵朋友幫手，叫佢上嚟聞吓臭成點，或者邊到最臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d65fb0b125e171a9f99315ee6b9fea895b8c3a8","tid":1001132,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d72906f900ecf406b83c3ba254a8eb5c5197b39","tid":1001132,"uid":76105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4dc472bb07138aae978c48ef8773991c205e556a","tid":1001132,"uid":32028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"你覺得係咪有味先, 定係人地玩野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"當你每日係哩個地方，你會適應咗果種味道。<br />\n你自己聞無味，但人地聞就好撚臭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:41:33.000Z","msg":"應該係話, 你有冇其他朋友去你屋企都覺得好勁"},{"pid":"a89bd2b4c7703bdfc0a147f7e1415ba8fdd71b4d","tid":1001132,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d65fb0b125e171a9f99315ee6b9fea895b8c3a8","tid":1001132,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d72906f900ecf406b83c3ba254a8eb5c5197b39","tid":1001132,"uid":76105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4dc472bb07138aae978c48ef8773991c205e556a","tid":1001132,"uid":32028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"你覺得係咪有味先, 定係人地玩野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"當你每日係哩個地方，你會適應咗果種味道。<br />\n你自己聞無味，但人地聞就好撚臭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:41:33.000Z","msg":"應該係話, 你有冇其他朋友去你屋企都覺得好勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:41:54.000Z","msg":"係樓主先岩"},{"pid":"9b90d3dfc6f457fe865a0a3c63b7b3a3a052529a","tid":1001132,"uid":1247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17599293293fe1580253edf665dab1e898ee165f","tid":1001132,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"可能問題唔係你隻狗身上，會唔會佢地痾咗屎尿係啲傢私裡面？<br />\n例如梳化，床，一啲木製傢品，牆，搞到啲味滲左入去，咁你點清都無用㗎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你都聞唔到 因為你聞慣，